sents: one night , a full moon out hung in the sky glowing with a red sheen . i could n't sleep , and headed outside for some fresh air .
wind whistled through the leafless trees , making an eerie sound . a shiver ran down my spine .
i heard someone coming down the path , making heavy footfalls . it sounded someone was heading straight for me , and fast .
panicking , i ducked behind a hill and threw some leaves over myself . i tried to stay perfectly still and quiet until the person passed by .
when i was sure all was safe , i made my way carefully back to the castle . i had to get inside and tell someone what had just happened .
